high_descs: Go to the right and turn around to face the end of the cabinet with the television on it.
Pick the watch up from the cabinet.
Go to the right and then turn to face the coffee table in front of the couch.
Put the watch on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a watch on a table.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the TV stand.
Pick up the watch from the stand.
Turn around and face the coffee table.
Put the watch on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put the watch on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn right, go straight, turn right, step forward, then turn right to face the table with the TV on it.
Pick up the watch on the table, to the right of the remote.
Turn right, move forward, turn left, move forward, then turn right to face the coffee table.
Put the watch on the front left corner of the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Move the watch to the coffee table.
